		</div>
		<div class="comment_text"><p>Well getAuthUser returns a username. You probably want to check len(...), not listLen, and CF8 added isLoggedIn() so you can check that. Also - you don't have to lock when you read/write session variables. "Lock everything" was the rule in CF5 and earlier days. Now you only lock when you have to worry about race conditions.</p></div>
